	dprr:hasNoteText "Leaders of the Plebs against Coriolanus (Liv. 2.33-35; Dion. Hal. 7.33.1-66.3; 8.31.4, Icilius; Plut. Cor. 13.1-21.4; cf. Fab. Pict. fr. 17, Peter; Gell. 17.21.11; Dio fr. 18; Eutrop. 1.15; Auct. Vir. Ill. 19; Zon. 7.16)." .
